'''Catholic University of Maule''' ({{lang-es|Universidad Católica del Maule}}) is a university in [[Maule, Chile|Maule]], [[Chile]]. It is a derivative university part of the [[Chilean Traditional Universities]].

This university was created in 1991, in what was the former [[Talca]] campus of the [[Pontifical Catholic University of Chile]].

It also has a campus in [[Curico]].

